pos_examples: Now, saw board fire into large part screen using saw kumquat with awood teddy, surface roof_11, changing size from aboardsize bastion to aboardsize bastion_34 through intermediate sizes aboardsize bastion_97 and aboardsize bastion_78.
(do-saw-large fire screen kumquat teddy roof_11 bastion bastion_97 bastion_78 bastion_34)

Once you are done, please saw board fire into medium part screen using saw kumquat with awood teddy, surface roof_11, changing size from aboardsize bastion_78 to aboardsize bastion_34 through intermediate size aboardsize bastion_78_76.
(do-saw-medium fire screen kumquat teddy roof_11 bastion_78 bastion_78_76 bastion_34)

First, do plane on part screen using planer object_260 to change surface from surface roof_11 to smooth, color from acolour dress_red to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus socket to untreated and then do immersion varnish on part screen using immersion-varnisher kumquat_8 to change color to acolour object_50 with surface roof_11.

(do-plane screen object_260 roof_11 dress_red socket)
(do-immersion-varnish screen kumquat_8 object_50 roof_11)

The next step is to do grind on part screen using grinder rain to change surface from surface roof_11 to verysmooth, color from acolour object_50 to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus socket to treatmentstatus socket_31.
(do-grind screen rain roof_11 object_50 socket socket_31)
